{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"30":"Chapters on Drinks"},"section_detail":{"30":{"hadithnumber_first":3371,"hadithnumber_last":3435,"arabicnumber_first":3371,"arabicnumber_last":3435}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3371,"arabicnumber":3371,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Darda’ : Mon ami proche (ﷺ) m’a conseillé : « Ne bois pas de vin, car c’est la clé de tous les maux. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":30,"hadith":1}}]}